531
00:47:50,829 --> 00:47:52,039
One more thing.

532
00:47:53,248 --> 00:47:54,875
I'm gonna need to look in your backpack.

533
00:47:57,961 --> 00:48:00,088
- [thrilling music playing]
- [both panting]

534
00:48:00,631 --> 00:48:01,632
[both grunting]

535
00:48:07,221 --> 00:48:08,388
[both exclaim]

