00:48:11,934 --> 00:48:12,934
[Ho-tae groans]

537
00:48:21,610 --> 00:48:22,694
[grunts]

538
00:48:33,789 --> 00:48:35,290
[suspenseful music playing]

539
00:49:14,454 --> 00:49:18,250
I'm sorry,
